{
  "id": "190",
  "title": "柱状图固定数据",
  "description": "画一个 5 柱的柱状图，数据为 [40, 70, 55, 90, 30]，柱宽 20，每柱颜色不同，底部对齐 y=-80。\n\n**输入格式：** 无输入。\n\n**输出格式：** 图形输出，5 根颜色不同的柱子和一条基线。",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "tags": [
    "坐标系",
    "moveTo",
    "统计",
    "循环"
  ],
  "starterCode": "// 先画基线，再用循环画每根柱子\n",
  "solution": "pen.c(0).size(1);\npen.moveTo(-110,-80).lineTo(110,-80);\npen.c(1); pen.moveTo(-80,-80).lineTo(-80,-40).lineTo(-60,-40).lineTo(-60,-80);\npen.c(2); pen.moveTo(-40,-80).lineTo(-40,-10).lineTo(-20,-10).lineTo(-20,-80);\npen.c(3); pen.moveTo(0,-80).lineTo(0,-25).lineTo(20,-25).lineTo(20,-80);\npen.c(4); pen.moveTo(40,-80).lineTo(40,10).lineTo(60,10).lineTo(60,-80);\npen.c(5); pen.moveTo(80,-80).lineTo(80,-50).lineTo(100,-50).lineTo(100,-80);",
  "hint": "每根柱子从底部 y=-80 往上延伸，高度由数据值决定。",
